		 <SETG P-NOT-HERE <+ ,P-NOT-HERE 1>>)>
	 <TELL "You can't see">
	 <COND (<OR <NOT .OBJ>
		    <AND .OBJ
			 <NOT <NAME? .OBJ>>>>
